Ask HN: Where to find mentors for staff+ engineers?
text:
I’m a staff engineer at a tech company but don’t have access to mentors that can guide me up into the higher levels of IC. I guess a distinguished engineer is what I’m looking for. I want to feel out what the track above me looks like in different companies, and what the day to day is like. I’d also like advice for how to navigate the increased income. I come from a family without money and am just now learning how to invest, for example.

Overall I really just want to know where are the people that are 5-10 years further along the path I’m on for camaraderie, advice, and stories.

Ask HN: Selling My Soul as an NFT
text: So my friend and I had this fun idea that we could let people mint & sell their 'souls' as NFT's. We plan to use authillo to prevent people from creating multiple accounts so users can only mint a single 'soul'. Ideally users would upload a picture of their face, and we'd do some AI art transformation to make their face into some randomized soul-like image. We've never developed any web3 applications so we're looking for a place to start... any suggestions? Also, has anyone come across a project like this already?
